Package: glottospace
Type: Package
Title: Language Mapping and Geospatial Analysis of Linguistic and Cultural Data
Version: 0.0.88
Author: Sietze Norder
Maintainer: Sietze Norder <mail@sietzenorder.nl>
Description: The glottospace R package facilitates the geospatial analysis of linguistic and cultural data. 
    The aim of the package is to provide a streamlined workflow for geolinguistic analysis, including: data import, 
    data entry, cleaning, exploration, mapping, visualization and export. Glottospace is 
    also intended as an R interface to global linguistic and cultural databases such as glottolog and WALS.
URL: https://github.com/SietzeN/glottospace
BugReports: https://github.com/SietzeN/glottospace/issues
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
